== 製作 ==
2014年2月6日，IFC電影公司宣布收購得到電影於[[北美|北美]]的播放權<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/02/ifc-acquires-kristen-stewart-guantanamo-bay-pic-camp-x-ray/|title=IFC Acquires Kristen Stewart Guantanamo Bay Pic ‘Camp X-Ray’|last=Fleming Jr|first=Mike|date=6 February 2014|newspaper=deadline.com|accessdate=7 February 2014}}</ref>。流星LLC收購了電影於阿拉伯聯合酋長國分發電影的權利。EDGE 娛樂將會在[[丹麥|丹麥]]、[[芬蘭|芬蘭]]、[[挪威|挪威]]及[[瑞典|瑞典]]分發電影的權利<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://en.edgeentertainment.se/film/camp-x-ray/|title=Camp X-Ray|accessdate=2 December 2014|publisher=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141014093124/http://en.edgeentertainment.se/film/camp-x-ray/|archivedate=2014年10月14日}}</ref>。這部影片於2014年10月30日於[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]]及[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]分發及上映。<span class="cx-segment" data-segmentid="224"></span>

=== 拍攝 ===
X射線營地攝於[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]及[[惠提爾|惠提爾]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://hollywoodlife.com/2013/07/12/kristen-stewart-set-camp-x-ray-good-vibes-joseph-julian-soria/|title=Kristen Stewart Starts Rehearsal For ‘Camp X-Ray’ With ‘Good Vibes’|date=12 July 2013|newspaper=hollywoodlife.com|accessdate=14 July 2013|archive-date=2013-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130714054212/http://hollywoodlife.com/2013/07/12/kristen-stewart-set-camp-x-ray-good-vibes-joseph-julian-soria/}}</ref>。主要的拍攝在2013年7月17日，並於8月中結束<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2013/07/13/camp-x-ray-starring-kristen-stewart-to-begin-filming-in-la/|title=‘Camp X-Ray’, starring Kristen Stewart, to begin filming in LA|date=13 July 2013|newspaper=onlocationvacations.com|accessdate=14 July 2013|archive-date=2014-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025045430/http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2013/07/13/camp-x-ray-starring-kristen-stewart-to-begin-filming-in-la/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=106610|title=Kristen Stewart Spott±ed on the Set of Camp X-Ray|date=18 July 2013|newspaper=comingsoon.net|accessdate=19 July 2013|archive-date=2014-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141014105244/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=106610}}</ref>。拍攝監獄場景的地點是加州惠蒂爾荒廢的弗雷德.C.尼爾斯青年懲教設施。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/tag/camp-x-ray-filming-locations/|title=Camp X-Ray filming locations|accessdate=2 December 2014|publisher=|archive-date=2014-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025045427/http://www.onlocationvacations.com/tag/camp-x-ray-filming-locations/}}</ref>

== 宣傳及營銷 ==
電影在2013年夏末到了後期製作。特別效果由Comen VFX製作<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.comenvfx.com/|title=Camp X-Ray gets in the Sundance 2014 U.S. Dramatic Competition.|accessdate=24 December 2013|archive-date=2022-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220430214104/http://comenvfx.com/}}</ref>。2013年12月5日，公司宣布電影將以美國戲劇競賽組別，於1月17日在[[聖丹斯電影節|聖丹斯電影節]]上映<ref>[http://filmguide.sundance.org/film/13908/camp_x-ray "Camp X-Ray"] {{Wayback|url=http://filmguide.sundance.org/film/13908/camp_x-ray |date=20131224114139 }}<span class="reference-accessdate"></ref>。在2014年7月3日，發放了10張電影的新劇照<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/new-images-from-kristen-stewarts-guantanamo-bay-drama-camp-x-ray-20140703|title=New Images From Kristen Stewart's Guantanamo Bay Drama 'Camp X-Ray'|date=July 3, 2014|publisher=indiewire.com|accessdate=July 4, 2014|last1=JAGERNAUTH|first1=KEVIN|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140707015259/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/new-images-from-kristen-stewarts-guantanamo-bay-drama-camp-x-ray-20140703|archive-date=2014-07-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。IFC電影公司於2014年8月8日在[[YouTube|YouTube]]頻道發布了官方預告片。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_1MDrwqjeGo|title=Camp X-Ray - Official Trailer - HD - IFC Films|accessdate=2 December 2014|work=YouTube|archive-date=2022-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220425025807/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_1MDrwqjeGo}}</ref>

《X射線營地》因為含有粗言及短暫的裸露影像而被[[美國電影協會|美國電影協會]]評為R級別<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ropeofsilicon.com/cinderella-camp-x-ray-november-man-red-army-todays-mpaa-ratings/|title='Cinderella', 'Camp X-Ray', 'November Man' & 'Red Army' in Today's MPAA Ratings|accessdate=2 December 2014|author=Brad Brevet|work=Rope of Silicon|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141013190809/http://www.ropeofsilicon.com/cinderella-camp-x-ray-november-man-red-army-todays-mpaa-ratings/|archive-date=2014-10-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。電影於2014年10月17日在被選的戲院及視頻點播服務上映，包括[[iTunes|iTunes]]電影及[[亞馬遜公司|Amazon.com]]視頻<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=campxray.htm|title=Camp X-Ray (2014) - Box Office Mojo|accessdate=2 December 2014|publisher=|archive-date=2014-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141120045234/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=campxray.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此電影也被大西洋電影節、[[多維爾美國電影節|多維爾美國電影節]]、[[倫敦影展|倫敦影展]]、阿布扎比電影節、萊頓國際電影節、霍夫國際電影節，及[[斯德哥爾摩電影節|斯德哥爾摩電影節]]上映<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://whatson.bfi.org.uk/lff/Online/default.asp?doWork::WScontent::loadArticle=Load&BOparam::WScontent::loadArticle::article_id=880151F7-CA08-4201-AE6D-13F64F8D827E&BOparam::WScontent::loadArticle::context_id=F121E367-8603-49A3-A8CA-81A79EC89959|title=Welcome to BFI Southbank online|accessdate=2 December 2014|publisher=|archive-date=2021-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210515120300/https://whatson.bfi.org.uk/lff/Online/default.asp?doWork::WScontent::loadArticle=Load&BOparam::WScontent::loadArticle::article_id=880151F7-CA08-4201-AE6D-13F64F8D827E&BOparam::WScontent::loadArticle::context_id=F121E367-8603-49A3-A8CA-81A79EC89959}}</ref>。

